Package: RNHLStats
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for NHL Data APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Henry", "Poole", email = "henrypoole@g.ucla.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R wrapper for the publicly accessible portions of both the NHL stats API and NHL records API. This package is based off of the API specification documented by Drew Hynes (https://gitlab.com/dword4/nhlapi). 
